'''安娜·西利亞·德哈瑪斯·卡索'''（{{lang-es|Ana Celia de Armas Caso}}，{{bd|1988年|4月30日}}）是一位[[古巴|古巴]]女演員。知名於2015年演出的首部美國電影《[[夜半女敲門|夜半女敲門]]》，之後又出演《{{link-en|惡夜殺機|Exposed (2016 film)}}》（2016年）、《[[光榮擂台|光榮擂台]]》（2016年）和《[[軍火狗|軍火狗]]》（2016年）。

2017年，她在受好評的新黑色科幻電影《[[銀翼殺手2049|銀翼殺手2049]]》中飾演[[人工智能|人工智能]]立體投影Joi而聞名<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.forbes.com/sites/markhughes/2017/10/05/review-blade-runner-2049-miraculously-accomplishes-the-impossible/#75765d5e6e4a |title = Review: 'Blade Runner 2049' Miraculously Accomplishes The Impossible |author = Mark Hughes |date = 2017-10-05 |publisher = Forbes |language = en |access-date = 2018-12-31 |archive-date = 2020-10-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201001025336/https://www.forbes.com/sites/markhughes/2017/10/05/review-blade-runner-2049-miraculously-accomplishes-the-impossible/#75765d5e6e4a |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/a12184443/ana-de-armas-2017-interview-blade-runner-2049/ |title = Ana de Armas Is Complex and Incredible in Blade Runner 2049 |author = Emily Poenisch, By |date = 2017-10-03 |publisher = Esquire |language = en |access-date = 2018-12-31 |archive-date = 2021-01-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210117102306/https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/a12184443/ana-de-armas-2017-interview-blade-runner-2049/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hollywoods-next-big-thing-blade-runner-2049-breakout-ana-de-armas-1044837 |title = Hollywood's Next Big Thing: 'Blade Runner 2049' Breakout Ana de Armas |author = Rebecca Ford |date = 2017-10-06 |publisher = The Hollywood Reporter |language = en |access-date = 2018-12-31 |archive-date = 2020-06-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200619074242/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hollywoods-next-big-thing-blade-runner-2049-breakout-ana-de-armas-1044837 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，并因她在电影《[[鋒迴路轉|鋒迴路轉]]》（2019年）中担任主角护士玛塔·卡布雷拉而获得好评。后者为她赢得了[[金球奖最佳音乐及喜剧类电影女主角|金球奖最佳音乐及喜剧类电影女主角]]的提名。

== 早期生活 ==
安娜·德哈瑪斯出生於[[古巴|古巴]][[北聖克魯斯|北聖克魯斯]]。她畢業於{{le|古巴國家劇院|National Theatre of Cuba|古巴國家戲劇學校}}。在18歲時，她搬到了[[西班牙|西班牙]]。

== 個人生活 ==
德哈瑪斯目前住在[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]的[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]。她在2011年时与西班牙演员{{link-en|馬克·克洛特|Marc Clotet}}结婚，2013年两人离婚。<ref>[https://www.elmundo.es/loc/2015/11/04/563a41ade2704ed2708b4598.html El primer desnudo de Ana de Armas en Hollywood junto a Keanu Reeves] {{Wayback|url=https://www.elmundo.es/loc/2015/11/04/563a41ade2704ed2708b4598.html |date=20200919001519 }}.elmundo.2015-11-04.[2020-03-13].</ref>2020年3月，她被报道在与美国著名演员[[本·阿弗莱克|本·阿弗莱克]]约会，两人之前在电影《[[深水_(2022年电影)|深水]]》中合演并相识。兩人於2021年1月分手。<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Russian|first=Ale|date=2021-01-18|title=Ben Affleck and Ana de Armas Split, Says Source: 'They Are in Different Points in Their Lives'|url=https://people.com/movies/ben-affleck-and-ana-de-armas-split-source/|magazine=People|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308161006/https://people.com/movies/ben-affleck-and-ana-de-armas-split-source/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite magazine|last=Crabtree|first=Erin|date=2021-01-18|title=Ben Affleck and Ana de Armas Split After Nearly 1 Year Together|magazine=US Magazine|url=https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/ben-affleck-girlfriend-ana-de-armas-split/|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204203819/https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/ben-affleck-girlfriend-ana-de-armas-split/}}</ref>

